#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:1
msgid "使用数据获取渠道自动填充数据"
msgstr "Automatically populate data using data acquisition channels."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:3
msgid ""
"前面介绍过`DataSource`对象的基本操作方法，但是在实际使用中，我们需要往`DataSource`对象中填充大量数据，如果使用前面章节介绍的`DataSource.update_table_data()`方法手动填充数据，这样的工作量是非常大的。"
msgstr ""
"We have introduced the basic operation methods of the `DataSource` object. "
"However, in actual use, we need to populate the `DataSource` object with a "
"large amount of data. If we manually populate the data using the "
"`DataSource.update_table_data()` method introduced in the previous chapter, "
"the workload will be very large."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:5
msgid "这里我们介绍如何使用数据获取渠道自动填充数据。"
msgstr ""
"Here we introduce how to use data acquisition channels to automatically "
"populate data."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:7
msgid "QTEASY数据拉取功能"
msgstr "QTEASY data retrieval function"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:9
msgid "`QTEASY`数据管理模块: ![数据获取模块结构](img/DataFetching.png)"
msgstr ""
"`QTEASY` Data Management Module: ![Data Fetching Module "
"Structure](img/DataFetching.png)"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:9
msgid "数据获取模块结构"
msgstr "Data acquisition module structure"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:11
msgid ""
"如上图所示，`qteasy`的数据功能分为三层，第一层包括多种数据下载接口，用于从网络数据提供商获取数据，这个过程称为`DataFetching`。"
msgstr ""
"As shown in the diagram above, `qteasy`'s data functionality is divided into"
" three layers. The first layer includes various data download interfaces for"
" obtaining data from online data providers; this process is called "
"`DataFetching`."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:13
msgid "数据拉取接口`refill_data_source()`"
msgstr "The data retrieval interface `refill_data_source()`"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:15
msgid ""
"`qteasy`提供了一个自动化数据下载接口`qteasy.refill_data_source()`，可以从多个不同的网络数据提供商拉取多种金融数据，满足不同用户的使用习惯。`qteasy`提供的数据拉取API具备强大的多线程并行下载、数据分块下载、下载流量控制和错误延时重试功能，以适应不同数据供应商各种变态的流量限制，同时数据拉取API可以方便地定期自动运行完成数据批量下载任务，不用担心错过高频数据。"
msgstr ""
"`qteasy` provides an automated data download interface "
"`qteasy.refill_data_source()`, which can pull various financial data from "
"multiple different online data providers to meet the usage habits of "
"different users. The data pull API provided by `qteasy` features powerful "
"multi-threaded parallel downloading, data chunking downloading, download "
"traffic control, and error delay retry functions to adapt to the various "
"unpredictable traffic limits of different data providers. At the same time, "
"the data pull API can easily and automatically run batch data download tasks"
" on a regular basis, so you don't have to worry about missing high-frequency"
" data."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:17
msgid ""
"下面先用一个例子解释如何使用`qteasy.refill_data_source()`接口自动填充数据。我们先创建一个不含数据的`DataSource`对象，并向其中填充最基本的数据。"
msgstr ""
"Let's first use an example to explain how to automatically populate data "
"using the `qteasy.refill_data_source()` interface. We'll start by creating a"
" `DataSource` object that doesn't contain any data, and then populate it "
"with the most basic data."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:37
msgid ""
"我们可以看到，`DataSource`对象中已经有了一些数据表，为了进行下面的测试，我们将首先删除`trade_calendar`以及`stock_daily`两张数据表中的数据，然后再使用数据拉取接口自动填充它们。"
msgstr ""
"As we can see, the `DataSource` object already contains some data tables. To"
" conduct the following tests, we will first delete the data from the "
"`trade_calendar` and `stock_daily` data tables, and then use the data "
"retrieval interface to automatically populate them."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:39
msgid "首先删除两张数据表，为了删除数据表，首先将数据源的`allow_drop_table`属性设置为`True`，然后再删除数据表。"
msgstr ""
"First, delete two data tables. To delete a data table, first set the "
"`allow_drop_table` attribute of the data source to `True`, and then delete "
"the data table."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:58
msgid "可以看到，`trade_calendar`和`stock_daily`两张数据表中的数据已经被删除。"
msgstr ""
"As you can see, the data in the `trade_calendar` and `stock_daily` tables "
"has been deleted."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:60
msgid ""
"接下来，我们使用`qteasy.refill_data_source()`接口自动填充数据，代码很简单，只有一行，剩下的工作`qteasy`会自动完成。"
msgstr ""
"Next, we will use the `qteasy.refill_data_source()` interface to "
"automatically populate the data. The code is very simple, with only one "
"line, and `qteasy` will do the rest automatically."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:79
msgid "拉取并填充数据后，可以检查数据已经下载成功了："
msgstr ""
"After pulling and populating the data, you can check that the data has been "
"downloaded successfully:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:146
msgid "数据拉取API的功能特性"
msgstr "Features of the Data Retrieval API"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:148
msgid "分析数据拉取的过程，我们可以看到，`qteasy`自动完成了下面的工作："
msgstr ""
"Analyzing the data retrieval process, we can see that `qteasy` automatically"
" completed the following tasks:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:150
msgid ""
"**自动查找依赖表** —— "
"虽然我们只指定了`stock_daily`数据表，但是`qteasy`自动检测到`trade_calendar`数据表也是空的，且`stock_daily`表依赖交易日历表，所以也自动填充了`trade_calendar`数据表。"
msgstr ""
"**Automatic Dependency Table Lookup** — Although we only specified the "
"`stock_daily` table, `qteasy` automatically detected that the "
"`trade_calendar` table was also empty, and since the `stock_daily` table "
"depends on the trading calendar table, it also automatically populated the "
"`trade_calendar` table."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:151
msgid ""
"**下载进度可视化** —— "
"`qteasy`提供了下载进度可视化，可以看到每个数据分块的下载进度，以及总体下载进度，过程中可以显示剩余时间，方便用户查看数据下载的情况。"
msgstr ""
"**Download Progress Visualization** — `qteasy` provides download progress "
"visualization, allowing users to see the download progress of each data "
"block, as well as the overall download progress. It also displays the "
"remaining time, making it easy for users to monitor the data download "
"status."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:152
msgid ""
"**大数据量自动分块** —— "
"上面的代码下载了2021年全年所有股票的日K线数据，这些数据量共有239万行，不管从任何数据渠道，这么大量的数据都不可能一次性下载下来，因此，`qteasy`自动将数据分块，每一块只有一天的数据，可以看到整年的数据被分成了243块，数据分块下载显著降低了每次网络申请的数据量，提高成功率且降低了被阻断的风险。"
msgstr ""
"**Automatic Data Chunking** — The code above downloaded daily candlestick "
"chart data for all stocks throughout 2021, totaling 2.39 million rows. "
"Regardless of the data source, such a massive amount of data cannot be "
"downloaded all at once. Therefore, `qteasy` automatically chunks the data, "
"with each chunk containing only one day's data. As you can see, the entire "
"year's data was divided into 243 chunks. This chunked download significantly"
" reduces the amount of data requested per network request, increasing the "
"success rate and reducing the risk of being blocked."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:153
msgid ""
"**多线程并行下载** —— 实行数据分块下载后，`qteasy`自动使用多线程并行下载，加快数据下载速度，243个数据分块并行下载总共耗时仅16秒。"
msgstr ""
"**Multi-threaded Parallel Download** — After implementing data chunking for "
"download, `qteasy` automatically uses multi-threaded parallel download to "
"speed up the data download process. The total time for downloading 243 data "
"chunks in parallel was only 16 seconds."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:155
msgid ""
"有了上面这些特性，`qteasy`的数据拉取功能可以满足几乎所有用户的数据获取需求，不管是下载大量数据，还是下载高频数据，`qteasy`都能提供高效的数据下载服务。"
msgstr ""
"With these features, `qteasy`'s data retrieval function can meet the data "
"acquisition needs of almost all users. Whether downloading large amounts of "
"data or high-frequency data, `qteasy` can provide efficient data download "
"services."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:157
msgid "当然，除了上面提到的这些特性之外，`qteasy`还提供了更多的功能特性，以针对下载过程中出现的各种状况，这些功能特性我们在后面会逐步介绍："
msgstr ""
"Of course, in addition to the features mentioned above, `qteasy` offers many"
" more features to address various situations that may arise during the "
"download process. We will introduce these features in detail later:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:159
msgid ""
"**多渠道下载** —— `qteasy`提供了多种数据下载渠道，很多数据表可以从多个不同的渠道下载，而且随着版本更新，数据拉取渠道也在不断增加。"
msgstr ""
"**Multi-channel download** — `qteasy` provides multiple data download "
"channels. Many data tables can be downloaded from multiple different "
"channels, and the number of data retrieval channels is constantly increasing"
" with each version update."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:160
msgid ""
"**流量控制** —— "
"有些数据渠道对数据下载有流量限制，`qteasy`提供了流量控制功能，可以限制数据下载的速度，即下载一定分块数量的数据后，可以暂停一段时间，例如每下载300个分块的数据，就暂停一分钟，避免被数据渠道封禁。"
msgstr ""
"**Traffic Control** — Some data channels have traffic limits on data "
"downloads. `qteasy` provides a traffic control function that can limit the "
"data download speed. That is, after downloading a certain number of data "
"chunks, you can pause for a period of time. For example, pause for one "
"minute after downloading 300 data chunks to avoid being blocked by the data "
"channel."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:161
msgid ""
"**错误重试** —— "
"有些数据渠道下载数据时，可能会出现网络错误，`qteasy`提供了错误重试功能，可以在下载失败后，自动重试下载，如果重试不成功，会延长重试等待时间再试，直到下载成功或超过重试次数并报错。"
msgstr ""
"**Error Retry** — When downloading data from some data sources, network "
"errors may occur. `qteasy` provides an error retry function, which can "
"automatically retry the download after a failure. If the retry is "
"unsuccessful, it will extend the retry waiting time and try again until the "
"download is successful or the number of retries is exceeded and an error is "
"reported."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:162
msgid ""
"**日志记录** —— "
"`qteasy`提供了数据下载日志记录功能，可以记录每次数据下载的详细信息，包括下载的数据量、下载的时间、下载的速度等，方便用户查看数据下载的情况。"
msgstr ""
"**Log Recording** — `qteasy` provides a data download log recording "
"function, which can record detailed information for each data download, "
"including the amount of data downloaded, the download time, the download "
"speed, etc., making it convenient for users to view the data download "
"status."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:164
msgid "多渠道拉取数据"
msgstr "Data pulled from multiple channels"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:166
msgid "`qteasy`提供了多种数据下载渠道，很多数据表可以从多个不同的渠道下载，而且随着版本更新，数据拉取渠道也在不断增加。"
msgstr ""
"`qteasy` offers multiple data download channels, allowing many data tables "
"to be downloaded from various channels. Moreover, with each version update, "
"the number of data retrieval channels continues to increase."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:168
msgid ""
"refill_data_source()接口的channel参数可以指定数据下载渠道，如果不指定，`qteasy`会自动选择一个默认的数据下载渠道`tushare`，但是用户也可以手动指定数据下载渠道，例如"
" ："
msgstr ""
"The `channel` parameter of the `refill_data_source()` interface can specify "
"the data download channel. If not specified, `qteasy` will automatically "
"select a default data download channel, `tushare`. However, users can also "
"manually specify the data download channel, for example:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:170
msgid "下面的代码尝试从`eastmoney`数据渠道下载`stock_daily`数据表从2025年最初两个月的日K线数据："
msgstr ""
"The following code attempts to download daily candlestick data from the "
"`stock_daily` data table for the first two months of 2025 from the "
"`eastmoney` data channel:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:188
msgid "验证一下数据是否下载成功："
msgstr "Verify that the data was downloaded successfully:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:244
msgid "数据下载显然也是成功的。分析上面的下载过程，可以发现几个特点："
msgstr ""
"The data download was clearly successful. Analyzing the download process "
"above, several characteristics can be observed:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:246
msgid ""
"不同渠道下载的数据格式是相同的，这是`qteasy`的设计原则，不同的数据下载渠道下载的数据会经历相同的清洗过程，这样用户可以方便地切换不同的数据下载渠道，而不用担心数据格式不同导致的数据处理问题。"
msgstr ""
"Data downloaded from different channels is in the same format. This is a "
"design principle of `qteasy`. Data downloaded from different channels will "
"undergo the same cleaning process. This allows users to easily switch "
"between different data download channels without worrying about data "
"processing problems caused by different data formats."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:247
msgid ""
"不同的渠道下载分块方式不同，导致下载速度不同，`eastmoney`数据渠道下载速度较慢，需要约17分钟才能下载完成。这是由于不同下载渠道的特殊限制决定的。"
msgstr ""
"Different download channels use different chunking methods, resulting in "
"varying download speeds. The `eastmoney` data channel is slower, taking "
"approximately 17 minutes to complete. This is due to the specific "
"limitations of each download channel."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:248
msgid ""
"不同渠道的下载可以下载的数据表也不同，有些数据表无法通过某些渠道下载，可能是因为权限限制或者其他因素导致的，如果某个数据表无法下载，`qteasy`会自动跳过这个数据表，不会影响其他数据表的下载。"
msgstr ""
"Different download channels may allow downloading different data tables. "
"Some data tables may not be downloadable through certain channels, possibly "
"due to permission restrictions or other factors. If a data table cannot be "
"downloaded, `qteasy` will automatically skip that data table without "
"affecting the download of other data tables."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:250
msgid "因此，用户需要根据自身的情况选择不同的渠道拉取数据。"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, users need to choose different channels to retrieve data based on"
" their own circumstances."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:252
msgid "实现下载流量控制"
msgstr "Implement download traffic control"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:254
msgid ""
"`qteasy`的`refill_data_source`提供了流量控制功能，可以限制数据下载的速度，即下载一定分块数量的数据后，可以暂停一段时间，例如每下载300个分块的数据，就暂停一分钟，避免被数据渠道封禁。"
msgstr ""
"`qteasy`'s `refill_data_source` provides a flow control function that can "
"limit the data download speed. That is, after downloading a certain number "
"of data chunks, it can pause for a period of time. For example, it can pause"
" for one minute after downloading 300 data chunks to avoid being blocked by "
"the data channel."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:256
msgid ""
"这个功能通过refill_data_source()接口的`download_batch_size`和`download_batch_interval`两个参数实现："
msgstr ""
"This functionality is achieved through the `download_batch_size` and "
"`download_batch_interval` parameters of the `refill_data_source()` "
"interface:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:258
msgid "`download_batch_size`参数指定每次下载的数据分块数量，如果设置为300，则在下载300个数据分块后，会暂停一段时间。"
msgstr ""
"The `download_batch_size` parameter specifies the number of data chunks "
"downloaded each time. If it is set to 300, the download will pause for a "
"period of time after downloading 300 data chunks."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:259
msgid "`download_batch_interval`参数指定每次下载数据分块后的暂停时间，默认为0，即不暂停。"
msgstr ""
"The `download_batch_interval` parameter specifies the pause time after each "
"data chunk is downloaded; the default value is 0, meaning no pause."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:261
msgid "下面的代码演示了如何使用`download_batch_size`和`download_batch_interval`参数实现下载流量控制："
msgstr ""
"The following code demonstrates how to implement download traffic control "
"using the `download_batch_size` and `download_batch_interval` parameters:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:275
msgid "如果是用流量控制，当然下载时间会变长，但是对于某些数据渠道，这是必须的，否则可能会被封禁或报错导致下载失败。"
msgstr ""
"If traffic control is used, the download time will naturally be longer, but "
"for some data channels, this is necessary; otherwise, the download may be "
"blocked or encounter errors, leading to download failure."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:277
msgid "实现错误重试"
msgstr "Implement error retries"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:279
msgid "需要注意的是，数据下载过程中出错，`qteasy`会自动重试下载，重试机制如下："
msgstr ""
"It should be noted that if an error occurs during the data download process,"
" `qteasy` will automatically retry the download. The retry mechanism is as "
"follows:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:281
msgid "第一次下载失败后重试之前会等待一段时间，默认等待时间为1.0秒"
msgstr ""
"After the first download fails, a short wait will occur before retrying; the"
" default wait time is 1.0 second."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:282
msgid "每次重试失败后，等待时间都会增加，默认等待时间增加为2倍，即第一次等待1.0秒，第二次等待2.0秒，第三次等待4.0秒，以此类推。"
msgstr ""
"Each time a retry fails, the waiting time will increase, with the default "
"waiting time increasing to twice the original value. That is, the first time"
" waits for 1.0 second, the second time waits for 2.0 seconds, the third time"
" waits for 4.0 seconds, and so on."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:283
msgid "重试超过最大限额后停止重试并报错，默认情况下最多重复7次。"
msgstr ""
"Retrying will stop and an error will be reported after the maximum number of"
" retries is exceeded. By default, the maximum number of retries is 7."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:285
msgid ""
"以上三个错误重试参数都是通过`qteasy`的配置文件在设定的，用户可以通过`qt.config()`接口查看或修改这些参数，也可以在`qteasy`的初始配置文件中修改这些参数。"
msgstr ""
"The above three error retry parameters are all set through the `qteasy` "
"configuration file. Users can view or modify these parameters through the "
"`qt.config()` interface, or they can modify these parameters in the initial "
"configuration file of `qteasy`."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:287
msgid "`hist_dnld_retry_cnt` - 最大重试次数，默认为7次"
msgstr "`hist_dnld_retry_cnt` - Maximum number of retries, defaults to 7."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:288
msgid "`hist_dnld_retry_wait` - 第一次重试等待时间，默认为1.0秒"
msgstr ""
"`hist_dnld_retry_wait` - The wait time for the first retry, the default is "
"1.0 second."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:289
msgid "`hist_dnld_backoff` - 重试等待时间增加倍数，默认为2.0"
msgstr ""
"`hist_dnld_backoff` - The multiplier for increasing the retry wait time; the"
" default is 2.0."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:291
msgid ""
"关于如何修改配置文件，或者使用`qteasy`的初始配置文件，请参考[`qteasy`的配置文件章节](../api/api_reference.rst)。"
msgstr ""
"For instructions on how to modify the configuration file, or to use the "
"initial configuration file for `qteasy`, please refer to the configuration "
"file section of `qteasy` (../api/api_reference.rst)."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:293
msgid "日志记录"
msgstr "Logging "

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:295
msgid ""
"`qteasy`提供了数据下载日志记录功能，可以记录每次数据下载的详细信息，包括下载的数据量、下载的时间、下载的速度等，方便用户查看数据下载的情况。"
msgstr ""
"`qteasy` provides a data download log recording function, which can record "
"detailed information for each data download, including the amount of data "
"downloaded, the download time, the download speed, etc., making it "
"convenient for users to check the data download status."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:297
msgid "其他功能"
msgstr "Other functions"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:299
msgid "`qteasy`的`refill_data_source()`接口还提供了其他一些功能，例如："
msgstr ""
"The `qteasy` `refill_data_source()` interface also provides other "
"functionalities, such as:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:301
msgid ""
"限制下载数据的范围，可以通过`start_date`和`end_date`参数限制下载数据的时间范围，通过`shares`参数限制下载数据的股票范围。"
msgstr ""
"To limit the range of downloaded data, you can use the `start_date` and "
"`end_date` parameters to restrict the time range of downloaded data, and the"
" `shares` parameter to restrict the range of stocks to be downloaded."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:302
msgid "设置是否并行下载，可以通过`parallel`参数设置是否并行下载，如果设置为False，则会串行下载，否则会并行下载。"
msgstr ""
"To configure whether to download in parallel, you can use the `parallel` "
"parameter. If set to False, downloads will be performed serially; otherwise,"
" they will be performed in parallel."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:303
msgid ""
"设置是否下载依赖表，可以通过`download_dependent`参数设置是否下载依赖表，如果设置为False，则不会下载依赖表，否则会下载依赖表。"
msgstr ""
"To configure whether to download dependency tables, you can use the "
"`download_dependent` parameter. If set to False, dependency tables will not "
"be downloaded; otherwise, they will be downloaded."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:304
msgid "设置是否强制更新交易日历表。"
msgstr "Configure whether to force an update of the transaction calendar."

#: ../../source/manage_data/4. data_channels.md:306
msgid "其他更多关于该接口的解释，请参见`qteasy`的[API文档](../api/history_data.rst)。"
msgstr ""
"For further explanation of this interface, please refer to the `qteasy` API "
"documentation (../api/history_data.rst)."
